    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing function over form. While the engine and transmission are dependable, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several paint scuffs, small door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use, and some interior trim pieces are loose. It is a solid, drivable car that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC or simply serve as a hardworking daily commuter.",
      "price": 18500.0,
