    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is the ultimate project car, offering a rare chance to bring a classic back to life from the ground up. While it currently requires extensive mechanical repairs and a full cosmetic refresh, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to build their dream ride exactly how they want it!",
      "price": 7500.0,
