    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a reliable and sophisticated driving experience. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the quality of this well-appointed selection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
